Subject: Continuous Delivery: Make Software Config and Deployment Quick and Painless
Description: We are going to explore continuous delivery as a solution to the arduous problems of configuration and deployment management. Begone long hours of painful, error-prone releases! This method should make config and deployment, painless, easy and quick. This is an intermediate level topic for those familiar with software development.  Speakers include:Mark Henke - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector

Subject: Tips and Tricks using ASP MVC 5
Description: We will be going through some lessons learned while using Asp Mvc over the year, including tricks like metadata conventions handling validation and dealing with dropdowns.  Speakers include:Mark Henke - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
